  "title": "Salty Mediterranean Tomato Stir-fry",
  "description": "A crispy and salty mediterranean dish featuring red chilli and other aromatic vegetables for a romantic twist that is also vegetarian-friendly.",
  "cuisine": "Mediterranean",
