  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a wok or large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add onions and garlic, sautéing until translucent and slightly golden.",
    "Add red chilli peppers and cook for another minute until fragrant.",
    "Stir in tomatoes (with their juice) and lemon juice. Let simmer for about 5 minutes to reduce the liquid slightly.",
    "Season with salt to taste. Mix in chopped parsley just before serving.",
    "Serve hot as a side dish or main course."
  ],
